.section *refid='nt' nt
.*
.ix 'nt'
.ix 'Block' 'nt'
.ix 'Generated text' 'nt'
.ix 'Notices' 'nt'
.tag begin
.tdesc
Begins a multi-paragraph note. All of the text in the note left aligns with the first word after the message
text. The text begins with a local-specific phrase ("Note:  " in the en_US locale).
.tclose ent
.tattrbs
.tattr text='text'
Substitute 'text' for the default "Note:  " phrase.
.tattrend
.tclass Block
.tcont Text, Formatting, In-line, Block, List-block
.tseealso
:HDREF refid='caution'., :HDREF refid='note'., :HDREF refid='warning'.
.tag end

